title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1982-05-21
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Friend Of The Devil, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Bird Song-> CC Rider, Althea-> Looks Like Rain, Might As Well

Set 2

Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Playin' In The Band-> Black Peter-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Don't Ease Me In

reviews.review_text: Very Good Love it sick show. Some might ask why 4 stars when I think its a good show or sick show. Is because they have had many a 5 star shows but I think more often then not they are in 1977 or 1968 threw 1972. That doesn't mean I think other years lack sick shows  these are just some of my favorite years.

Excellent show and superb maxtrix This is a really fine show.  The Playin' --> UJB is really cool, as is The Wheel and Black Peter segment.  

The fidelity is a joy.  Thanks Dave Usborne--you do an incredible job.
